---
title: Pizza-Style Chicken with Arugula and Spinach Salad
description: Tonight is pizza night, without the dough! Top tender butterflied chicken breasts with marinara and gooey melted cheese for a taste of delicious pizza-pie. Fresh cabbage and sweet peppers add bright balance to a peppery arugula side salad.

